{"type":"message","id":"fae7bba5","parentId":"67a67b1c","timestamp":"2026-04-22T01:49:13.968Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b51b6df4d24b8c36f369060b01ae\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_48df4034f5d6d43826ed1c5cf3e2ab69\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_48df4034f5d6d43826ed1c5cf3e2ab69\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-04-22 09:49 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_48df4034f5d6d43826ed1c5cf3e2ab69\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_48df4034f5d6d43826ed1c5cf3e2ab69\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_48df4034f5d6d43826ed1c5cf3e2ab69\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b51b6df4d24b8c36f369060b01ae]\nou_48df4034f5d6d43826ed1c5cf3e2ab69: 你现在的搜索功能是如何实现的？\n\n[System: The content may include mention tags in the form <at user_id=\"...\">name</at>. Treat these as real mentions of Feishu entities (users or bots).]\n[System: If user_id is \"ou_ccee94c267e8f9d0b4e40d93a0f54a77\", that mention refers to you.]"}],"timestamp":1776822553968}}
{"type":"message","id":"16cd09b7","parentId":"fae7bba5","timestamp":"2026-04-22T01:49:18.284Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问搜索功能如何实现的，需要解释我的搜索能力是通过 memory_search 工具调用 MEMORY.md 和记忆文件来实现的。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我目前的搜索功能主要通过以下方式实现：\n\n## 📖 记忆搜索\n\n使用 `memory_search` 工具在 **MEMORY.md** + **memory/*.md** 文件中做语义搜索：\n\n- **query**: 搜索关键词\n- **maxResults**: 最多返回结果数（默认未设）\n- **minScore**: 最低匹配分数\n- **corpus**: \n  - `memory` — 只搜本地记忆文件（默认）\n  - `wiki` — 加上知识库补充\n  - `all` — 全部范围\n\n## 📝 精确读取\n\n使用 `memory_get` 读取特定文件的指定段落：\n\n```bash\nmemory_get(path=\"memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md\", from=1, lines=10)\n```\n\n## ⚠️ 限制\n\n1. **只在主会话加载 MEMORY.md** — 群聊/共享场景不加载，避免隐私泄露\n2. **搜索结果有截断** — 文件超过 2000 行或 50KB 会 truncation\n3. **依赖已有文件** — 如果信息没写入文件，搜索不到\n\n---\n\n如果你需要我帮你查某个具体事情，直接说关键词就行～ 🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":23258,"output":322,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23580,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776822553968,"responseId":"chatcmpl-17364bdb-d70d-9505-b285-cdb75024e13f"}}
