{"type":"message","id":"84d99b89","parentId":"64db1587","timestamp":"2026-04-22T01:49:37.266Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b51b6dc3ca0a4c3aff613236591e\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_48df4034f5d6d43826ed1c5cf3e2ab69\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_48df4034f5d6d43826ed1c5cf3e2ab69\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-04-22 09:49 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_48df4034f5d6d43826ed1c5cf3e2ab69\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_48df4034f5d6d43826ed1c5cf3e2ab69\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_48df4034f5d6d43826ed1c5cf3e2ab69\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b51b6dc3ca0a4c3aff613236591e]\nou_48df4034f5d6d43826ed1c5cf3e2ab69: 我说的是联网搜索功能。\n\n[System: The content may include mention tags in the form <at user_id=\"...\">name</at>. Treat these as real mentions of Feishu entities (users or bots).]\n[System: If user_id is \"ou_ccee94c267e8f9d0b4e40d93a0f54a77\", that mention refers to you.]"}],"timestamp":1776822577266}}
{"type":"message","id":"d31689d6","parentId":"84d99b89","timestamp":"2026-04-22T01:49:43.303Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问的是联网搜索功能，我需要解释 agent-reach 技能提供的网络访问能力。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"哦明白了！你说的**联网搜索**我是这样实现的：\n\n## 🔍 联网搜索工具\n\n### 1. `web_fetch` — 轻量级网页抓取\n\n适合快速提取单个 URL 的内容：\n\n```python\nweb_fetch(url=\"https://example.com\", extractMode=\"markdown\")\n```\n\n- **用途**：获取文章、页面、文档的 markdown/text 格式内容\n- **特点**：HTML → Markdown 自动转换，支持截断 (`maxChars`)\n- **限制**：不适合复杂交互（需要登录、表单提交等场景）\n\n---\n\n### 2. `browser` — 完整浏览器控制\n\n适合复杂场景：\n\n```python\nbrowser(action=\"snapshot\", refs=\"aria\")  # 截图 + 识别可操作元素\nbrowser(action=\"act\", kind=\"click\", ref=\"e123\")  # 点击\nbrowser(action=\"act\", kind=\"type\", text=\"search query\")  # 输入\n```\n\n- **用途**：模拟真人浏览、处理登录/验证码/动态加载页面\n- **模式**：`openclaw` (隔离浏览器) / `user` (本地用户浏览器)\n- **支持**：导航、截图、PDF、文件上传、对话框处理等\n\n---\n\n### 3. [agent-reach](file:///Users/zhu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/agent-reach/SKILL.md) — 多平台接入（如果有权限）\n\n这是一个专门的网络访问技能，支持 **17 个平台**的 CLI/MCP/curl/Python 脚本对接：\n\n- **社交媒体**：小红书 / 抖音 / 微博 / 推特 / B 站 / V2EX / Reddit\n- **职业发展**：LinkedIn\n- **代码平台**：GitHub\n- **内容平台**：公众号 / RSS / 通用网页\n- **视频平台**：YouTube / B 站 / 播客\n\n如果你有配置相关平台的 API Key，可以直接调用对应的路由命令。\n\n---\n\n## 📌 总结\n\n| 需求 | 推荐工具 |\n|------|----------|\n| 简单网页内容 | `web_fetch` |\n| 需要交互/登录 | `browser` |\n| 特定平台深度操作 | [agent-reach](file:///Users/zhu/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/agent-reach/SKILL.md) |\n\n老板你具体想看什么内容？我帮你查～ 🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":24112,"output":568,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24680,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776822577266,"responseId":"chatcmpl-e34532e8-8898-9504-b308-165be1a9bba0"}}
