{"type":"message","id":"c3e93c4d","parentId":"ce5fb400","timestamp":"2026-04-22T05:46:57.306Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"已经成功保存了 agent-browser 技能的内容到 memory/browser-skill.md 文件，现在需要告诉用户保存完成，并提供快速索引方便查阅。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **Agent Browser (clawdbot) 技能已保存！**\n\n已将完整的技能说明保存到：\n- 📄 `/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/general_manager_shrimp/memory/browser-skill.md`\n\n---\n\n## 📋 核心要点速览\n\n| 功能 | 关键命令 |\n|------|----------|\n| 打开网页 | `agent-browser open <url>` |\n| 快照（必备） | `agent-browser snapshot -i --json` |\n| 点击元素 | `agent-browser click @e2` |\n| 填充文本 | `agent-browser fill @e3 \"text\"` |\n| 等待加载 | `agent-browser wait --load networkidle` |\n| 会话隔离 | `--session admin/user` |\n| 保存认证 | `state save/load auth.json` |\n| 截图/PDF | `screenshot` / `pdf` |\n\n---\n\n**Ref 机制是核心**：用 `@e1`, `@e2` 引用确保确定性选择，比传统 XPath/CSS Selector 更稳定。\n\n随时调用！🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":33985,"output":307,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34292,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776836814847,"responseId":"chatcmpl-f7be2e59-e3ec-9b20-b8f3-5633e474fe80"}}
