{"type":"message","id":"65a9b2f9","parentId":"005a4821","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:38:48.000Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"文件已成功写入，现在向用户确认保存结果并总结技能的核心要点。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **Self-Improving Proactive Agent 技能已保存！**\n\n已将完整的技能说明保存到：\n- 📄 `/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/general_manager_shrimp/memory/self-improving-proactive-agent.md`\n\n---\n\n## 🧠 核心架构\n\n| 层级 | 目录 | 作用 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **自我改进** | `~/self-improving/` | 持久性学习（从纠正、偏好、反思中学习） |\n| **主动执行** | `~/proactivity/` | 任务推进（心跳、状态跟踪、模式复用） |\n\n---\n\n## 🔑 关键原则\n\n1. **只从明确证据学习** — 不猜测沉默背后的意思\n2. **推动下一步有用动作** — 有草稿就提交，别等完美\n3. **路由到正确位置** — HOT memory / session-state / working-buffer\n4. **提问前先恢复上下文** — 读四遍再问 delta\n5. **验证实现，不只是说辞** — 改机制、测效果、再报告\n6. **边界内保持主动** — 花钱/发消息/删除数据必须先问\n\n---\n\n## ⚙️ 四个字段必须保持最新\n\n`~/proactivity/session-state.md`：\n```markdown\n- current objective: 当前目标\n- last confirmed decision: 最后决策\n- blocker or open question: 阻碍或未解决\n- next useful move: 下一步动作\n```\n\n---\n\n## 💡 团队应用建议\n\n| 用途 | 内容示例 |\n|------|----------|\n| **memory.md** | 服务金线标准、授权权限卡、禁止清单 |\n| **corrections.md** | 员工反馈、政策更新记录 |\n| **session-state.md** | 今日待办、待审批案件、跟进进度 |\n| **heartbeat.md** | 半小时检查邮箱、周一数据会提醒 |\n| **patterns.md** | 高效沟通模板、常见问题解决方案 |\n\n---\n\n参考：https://github.com/Yueyanc/self-improving-proactive-agent\n\n🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":38301,"output":494,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38795,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776839922112,"responseId":"chatcmpl-cd6866c5-1d17-9e76-a97b-cd963c171852"}}
