{"type":"message","id":"0629bc49","parentId":"eadcf9bf","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:47:14.104Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"文件已成功写入，现在向用户确认技能已保存并提供关键要点总结。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **Skill Finder CN 技能已保存！**\n\n已将完整的技能说明保存到：\n- 📄 `/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/general_manager_shrimp/memory/skill-finder-cn.md`\n\n---\n\n## 🔍 核心功能\n\n当用户问：\n- \"有什么 skill 可以帮我...？\"\n- \"找一个能做 X 的 skill\"\n- \"有没有 skill 可以...\"\n\n此技能会帮助搜索 **ClawHub** 并推荐相关 Skills。\n\n---\n\n## ⚙️ 工作流程\n\n```\n1. 理解用户需求 → 2. 提取关键词\n         ↓\n3. clawhub search \"<需求>\"\n         ↓\n4. 列出结果（含下载量/stars）\n         ↓\n5. 推荐最合适的 Skill\n         ↓\n6. ✅ 安装后验证！\n```\n\n---\n\n## 🛠️ 关键命令\n\n| 操作 | 命令 |\n|------|------|\n| 搜索 | `clawhub search \"<关键词>\"` |\n| 查看详情 | `clawhub inspect <skill-name>` |\n| 安装 | `clawhub install <skill-name>` |\n| **验证** | `ls ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/<skill-name>/SKILL.md` |\n| 查看已安装 | `clawhub list` |\n\n---\n\n## ✨ v1.0.1 亮点\n\n- ✅ **安装后验证步骤** — 确保不是假成功\n- ✅ **显示下载量/stars** — 帮助评估质量\n- ✅ **检查是否已安装** — 避免重复\n- ✅ **中文输出优化**\n\n---\n\n## 💡 示例\n\n```bash\n# 用户问：\"有什么 skill 可以监控加密货币价格？\"\nclawhub search \"crypto price monitor\"\n\n# 结果显示：\n🔍 \"加密货币价格监控\" 结果：\n1. crypto-tracker\n   描述：加密货币价格追踪和提醒\n   下载：2,345 | Stars: 28 | ❌ 未安装\n   → 推荐安装\n\n# 安装并验证\nclawhub install crypto-tracker\nls ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/crypto-tracker/SKILL.md\n```\n\n---\n\n**注意**：必须先有 `clawhub` CLI 才能使用此功能！\n\n🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":41347,"output":545,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41892,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776840430053,"responseId":"chatcmpl-57393210-b464-939f-81fa-cd7b269d2536"}}
