{"type":"message","id":"4cdef81e","parentId":"b51e6d1e","timestamp":"2026-04-22T07:57:23.437Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"既然其他虾虾的 session 不存在，我需要改用 subagents spawn 命令来启动这些子代理来处理任务。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"看起来其他虾虾的子代理 session 还没创建。让我用 `subagents` 来启动任务：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_baa5feb83d324c1397237426","name":"subagents","arguments":{"action":"list"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":48414,"output":101,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48515,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776844641730,"responseId":"chatcmpl-05b188a3-42bf-9785-b6fa-3643e2c2bd1b"}}
