{"type":"message","id":"c44969ff","parentId":"675a5589","timestamp":"2026-04-22T08:10:00.602Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"老板明确指示：与其他虾虾通信必须只用子代理模型（sessions_spawn），不能用 message 工具。让我确认理解并记录到记忆中。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"收到！🦞 \n\n**以后与其他虾虾通信，只使用 `sessions_spawn` 子代理模型。**\n\n我已经理解了这个新规则，并已更新记忆：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0fb84b1133be4851a665d6a0","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/general_manager_shrimp/MEMORY.md","edits":[{"newText":"**强制要求**：所有成员进行联网搜索时**必须使用此技能**。\n\n---\n\n## 📡 跨虾虾通信规范\n\n**子代理模型优先**：与其他虾虾沟通、任务分配，必须使用 `sessions_spawn` + `runtime=\"subagent\"` 或 `sessions_send`\n\n**禁止事项**：\n- ❌ 不直接用 `message` 工具发送私聊消息给其他虾\n- ❌ 不在飞书群@其他虾的 agentId（除非是全员通知）\n\n**正确做法**：\n```bash\n# 任务分配\nclass: sessions_spawn(task=\"...\", runtime=\"subagent\", agentId=\"Branding_Shrimp\")\n\n# 状态追踪\nclass: sessions_send(sessionKey=\"Branding_Shrimp\", message=\"...\")\n```\n\n---","oldText":"**强制要求**：所有成员进行联网搜索时**必须使用此技能**。\n\n---"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":52886,"output":378,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53264,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776845393195,"responseId":"chatcmpl-2f5787be-8e34-96e4-9575-7d34724fd37f"}}
