{"type":"message","id":"bb52b630","parentId":"89f28a2d","timestamp":"2026-04-22T08:11:40.344Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看起来 subagent 没有持久化。这是因为 sessions_spawn 默认是 run mode，一次性任务执行完就结束了。我需要用 mode=\"session\" 来创建持久会话。\n\n但是之前的调用虽然报了 Feishu binding error，但实际上已经返回了 childSessionKey，说明 session 被创建了只是绑定失败了。\n\n让我尝试用 `sessions_send` 方式来给各虾虾发送任务消息，看看哪些 session 可用：\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"让我用 `sessions_send` 给已创建的子代理发送任务消息：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d09291655a1b4266be60057d","name":"sessions_send","arguments":{"message":"@1 号品牌展示虾 🦐\n\n【绿色食品认证专项任务】\n- 官网新增绿色食品宣传板块\n- 准备 3 条朋友圈预热文案\n- 设计小红书对比图（普通食材 vs 绿色认证）\n- 线上门店添加\"已获认证\"标识\n\n优先级：⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐  今日完成初稿","sessionKey":"Branding_Shrimp","timeoutSeconds":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":60289,"output":329,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60618,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776845490739,"responseId":"chatcmpl-ea4c9cee-2d80-9ce6-84b3-3f06bac6cc4c"}}
