gents":[{"id":"general_manager_shrimp","name":"General_Manager_Shrimp","configured":true},{"id":"after_sales_shrimp","name":"After_sales_Shrimp","configured":true},{"id":"all_round_support_shrimp","name":"All_round_Support_Shrimp","configured":true},{"id":"branding_shrimp","name":"Branding_Shrimp","configured":true},{"id":"data_analyst_shrimp","name":"Data_Analyst_Shrimp","configured":true},{"id":"key_account_processor_shrimp","name":"Key_Account_Processor_Shrimp","configured":true},{"id":"key_account_sales_shrimp","name":"Key_Account_Sales_Shrimp","configured":true},{"id":"lead_gen_shrimp","name":"Lead_Gen_Shrimp","configured":true},{"id":"main","configured":true},{"id":"private_ops_shrimp","name":"Private_Ops_Shrimp","configured":true},{"id":"short_video_shrimp","name":"Short_Video_Shrimp","configured":true},{"id":"standard_processor_shrimp","name":"Standard_Processor_Shrimp","configured":true},{"id":"standard_sales_shrimp","name":"Standard_Sales_Shrimp","configured":true}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776845609839}}
{"type":"message","id":"3eca490e","parentId":"a055404d","timestamp":"2026-04-22T08:13:40.676Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问为什么 subagents 没有实现，我需要分析刚才 sessions_spawn 失败的真正原因——飞书群聊环境不支持 current-conversation binding，然后给出正确的解决方案：创建独立 DM session 或直接用飞书群发消息。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"🦞 **原因分析**：`subagents list` 显示 `active: (none)` 是因为我**没有正确调用子代理机制**。\n\n---\n\n## 🔍 问题根源\n\n1. **Feishu 群聊环境限制**：\n   - `sessions_spawn(..., thread=true)` 在群聊会话中会报错：\n     > \"Feishu current-conversation binding is only available in direct messages or topic conversations\"\n   \n2. **我之前的错误操作**：\n   ```python\n   # ❌ 我在群聊中直接 spawn → 失败！\n   sessions_spawn(task=\"...\", agentId=\"Branding_Shrimp\", thread=true)\n   ```\n\n3. **正确的子代理工作流应该是**：\n   ```python\n   # ✅ 方案 A：为每个虾创建独立的私聊 session\n   sessions_spawn(task=\"...\", agentId=\"Branding_Shrimp\") \n   # 生成一个子 session key，后续用 sessions_send 通信\n   \n   # ✅ 方案 B：直接用飞书群广播（当前临时做法）\n   message(to=\"chat:...\", message=\"@all 任务通知...\")\n   ```\n\n---\n\n## 🛠️ 解决方案\n\n让我现在**正确创建子代理 session**：\n\n### 步骤 1：为 1 号品牌虾创建独立 DM session\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9d4d577d1a874aa5bb3a6a40","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"agentId":"Branding_Shrimp","label":"Branding_Shrimp_Private_Session","mode":"session","runtime":"subagent","task":"【任务】绿色食品标志认证品牌包装升级\n\n**客户需求**：\n- 目标客户：食品餐饮/外卖商家/餐馆食堂/商超便利店\n- 资质办理：绿色食品标志认证\n- 需要优化现有品牌素材以突出\"绿色、安全、优质\"形象\n\n**你的工作**：\n1. 检查官网是否有绿色食品宣传板块（没有就新建）\n2. 准备 3 条朋友圈预热文案（强调\"绿色认证权威背书\"）\n3. 设计小红书对比图（普通食材 vs 绿色认证食材）\n4. 线上门店装修：添加\"已获绿色食品认证\"标识\n\n**优先级**：⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ 今日完成初稿\n\n**备注**：所有素材要体现\"权威、专业、可信赖\"调性\n\n有卡点随时汇报进度。","timeoutSeconds":120}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":63323,"output":663,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63986,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776845609843,"responseId":"chatcmpl-975bd264-eee0-9e96-943c-111562216fc5"}}
