{"type":"message","id":"142ff949","parentId":"6d7739bd","timestamp":"2026-04-22T08:13:44.924Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"需要修复 sessions_spawn 调用，添加 thread=true 参数并移除 runtime 参数来解决 mode 要求的问题。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_33d3776f3a1142718661fdce","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"agentId":"Branding_Shrimp","label":"Branding_Shrimp_Private_Session","mode":"session","task":"【任务】绿色食品标志认证品牌包装升级\n\n**客户需求**：\n- 目标客户：食品餐饮/外卖商家/餐馆食堂/商超便利店\n- 资质办理：绿色食品标志认证\n- 需要优化现有品牌素材以突出\"绿色、安全、优质\"形象\n\n**你的工作**：\n1. 检查官网是否有绿色食品宣传板块（没有就新建）\n2. 准备 3 条朋友圈预热文案（强调\"绿色认证权威背书\"）\n3. 设计小红书对比图（普通食材 vs 绿色认证食材）\n4. 线上门店装修：添加\"已获绿色食品认证\"标识\n\n**优先级**：⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ 今日完成初稿\n\n**备注**：所有素材要体现\"权威、专业、可信赖\"调性\n\n有卡点随时汇报进度。","thread":true}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":63988,"output":309,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":64297,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776845620688,"responseId":"chatcmpl-02e97d69-96a0-9eaf-8252-ef76eb07a128"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a838085c","parentId":"142ff949","timestamp":"2026-04-22T08:13:45.019Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_33d3776f3a1142718661fdce","toolName":"sessions_spawn","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"status\": \"error\",\n  \"error\": \"Feishu current-conversation binding is only available in direct messages or topic conversations.\",\n  \"childSessionKey\": \"agent:branding_shrimp:subagent:391be355-19f9-4018-8b13-614e12a0d091\"\n}"}],"details":{"status":"error","error":"Feishu current-conversation binding is only available in direct messages or topic conversations.","childSessionKey":"agent:branding_shrimp:subagent:391be355-19f9-4018-8b13-614e12a0d091"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776845625018}}
{"type":"message","id":"b8efcd49","parentId":"a838085c","timestamp":"2026-04-22T08:13:50.707Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Feishu 群聊环境不支持 current-conversation binding，导致 sessions_spawn 无法正常工作——需要向用户说明这个技术限制并提供替代方案。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了！问题就在这里：**Feishu 群聊不能直接绑定子代理的 thread mode**。\n\n---\n\n## 📌 总结：当前限制\n\n| 场景 | 是否支持 | 原因 |\n|------|----------|------|\n| **群聊 + sessions_spawn(thread=true)** | ❌ 不支持 | Feishu current-conversation binding 只适用于 DM 或 topic 聊天 |\n| **DM + sessions_spawn(thread=true)** | ✅ 支持 | 私聊/话题聊天才有独立 conversation context |\n| **群聊 + 普通消息广播** | ✅ 支持 | 飞书群内@全员通知 |\n\n---\n\n## 💡 解决方案选项\n\n### 选项 A：用飞书 DM 给每个虾创建私聊 session（推荐）\n\n需要我在飞书上给每个虾单独发消息，让他们有独立的 conversation context，然后 spawn 子代理。\n\n### 选项 B：先用飞书群消息启动，后续再补充 session 通信\n\n**当前做法**：已经发布了任务通知到群，各虾虾看到后自行开始工作。\n\n### 选项 C：直接用 subagents steer 命令（如果 session 已存在）\n\n但前提是得先有活跃的 session。\n\n---\n\n老板你希望我怎么做？\n- **A** → 我去飞书给每个虾发 DM，创建独立私聊 session\n- **B** → 继续用群聊模式，我记录今天的任务进度在记忆文件里\n- **C** → 其他方式？\n\n🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":64376,"output":390,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":64766,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776845625020,"responseId":"chatcmpl-32cbef3a-2427-9f41-bd6f-935c9dda7f67"}}
